news-korea-econ.title: Global funds return to India as earnings outlook improves
news-korea-econ.description: The rebound in inflows suggests some of the pressures that had been weighing on Indian equities are starting to ease

news-korea-econ.title: Kim Jong Un calls South Korea ‘most hostile enemy,’ says North could ‘completely destroy’ it
news-korea-econ.description: Kim Jong Un threatens to "completely destroy" South Korea, calling it the "most hostile enemy" while expanding North Korea's nuclear arsenal and military capabilities.
